{"sections":[],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L982"},"role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","text":"MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl","text":"UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the specified annotation."}]}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"control","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The control that was tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you specify is a descendant of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class, the map view calls this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view via the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"type":"text","text":" method, you can specify the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom accessory views using the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"leftAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rightAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}]},{"anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples","type":"heading","level":4},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:":{"title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/ml